summary.en: This garment is made from sustainable cotton which aims at improving the livelihood and economic status of people in cotton producing areas. While securing the future of the sector, sustainable cotton also reduces the environmental impact of cotton production.

summary.en: For a luxurious leisure look, this pair of trousers by Rina is a spectacular option. The captivating colour and textured finish uplift the appeal of these pants. It features drawstring closure across the waistband while the tailor-made construction from handpicked fabric makes it highly comfortable to wear. Moreover, coordinate these trousers with a bomber jacket and sneakers for an exceptional style.
